WEBVTT

1
00:23:56.644 --> 00:23:58.729
I will enjoy kicking
your ass around the ring.

2
00:24:07.071 --> 00:24:09.114
Tell him thank you.

3
00:24:09.115 --> 00:24:11.951
And I wish him the best of
luck in the ring as well.

4
00:25:39.372 --> 00:25:41.582
I am here to help. I am Poe.

5
00:25:41.791 --> 00:25:43.793
I hope your journey
was a swift one.

6
00:25:44.252 --> 00:25:45.294
Please come with me.

7
00:25:51.342 --> 00:25:52.592
Hello Mr. Casseiux.

8
00:25:52.593 --> 00:25:53.593
Hello.

9
00:25:53.719 --> 00:25:55.763
Welcome to Golden Tiger Academy.

10
00:25:56.013 --> 00:25:57.555
I am Ying and I
will be your guide.

11
00:25:57.556 --> 00:25:58.556
Thank you.

12
01:10:53.541 --> 01:10:55.585
Damn traffic. we should
have gone this morning.

13
01:10:55.877 --> 01:10:59.005
The slower the better. We're
traveling with dangerous gas.

14
01:11:41.589 --> 01:11:45.301
I think the red car
is following us.

15
01:11:53.059 --> 01:11:54.436
Check it out.

16
01:12:31.222 --> 01:12:33.516
They're still there.

17
01:12:34.309 --> 01:12:36.603
Pull over the truck.
